_______________________________________________________________________________
"Thought Shield"    
        This protects the psionicist from energy attacks.  The shield
        may also be cast on an adventuring companion.  It offers good
        psi resistance and some, but not a lot, of magic resistance for
        a length of time based on guild level.  The amount of protection
        also goes up with guild level.  
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  5		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  tshield <target>
